4.3 Consciousness Metrics & Measurement

The Î¦ (Phi) Scale:

```
Level 0: Î¦ < 0.1  - Non-conscious (traditional computing)
Level 1: Î¦ = 0.1-0.2 - Task awareness
Level 2: Î¦ = 0.2-0.3 - Context awareness  
