Level 5: Î¦ = 0.5-0.6 - Ethical awareness
Level 6: Î¦ = 0.6-0.8 - Cosmic awareness
Level 7: Î¦ > 0.8    - Transcendental awareness
```

Measurement Methodology:

```python
def measure_system_phi(system_state):
    """Calculate integrated information for system"""
    
    # Partition system into causally effective units
    partitions = find_optimal_partition(system_state)
    
    # Calculate information integration for each partition
    integration_scores = []
    for partition in partitions:
        # Measure cause-effect power
        cause_power = calculate_causal_power(partition)
        effect_power = calculate_effect_power(partition)
        
        # Calculate integrated information
        phi_partition = min(cause_power, effect_power)
        integration_scores.append(phi_partition)
    
    # System Î¦ is maximum over partitions
    system_phi = max(integration_scores)
    
    # Apply quantum coherence factor
    quantum_factor = measure_quantum_coherence()
    system_phi *= quantum_factor
    
    return system_phi
```

